      "content": "1000mg? the bottle says not to go over 800 in one go. are u sure that's okay? also i have some extra strength pills in the cabinet, would it be safer to just do a higher dose of those instead of mixing in aspirin? i'm really worried about my stomach but the pain is so bad i don't know what to do.",
